{
  "text": "It is unlikely that these results reflect only the connotative meanings highlighted by sensation-related adjectives, because reading or listening to sentences describing a behaviour causes an involuntary partial reactivation of the described experience ( [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] ; among others).",
  "correct_citation": {
